            <div type="assignment" facs="#image_027">
                <p> Þegar talad er um lögmálið, <lb break="yes"/>þá er það venjulega lög þau <lb break="yes"/>er gud gaf gydíngum fyrir Moísés <lb break="yes"/>á Sínai
                    fjalli, <del hand="#student">en</del>
                    <supplied><pc force="weak">.</pc></supplied> midudu <add place="above"
                        hand="#student">þau</add> til <lb break="yes"/>þess, ad halda vid <unclear
                        reason="hand" hand="#student">þekk</unclear>íngunni á <lb break="yes"/>þeim
                    eina sama gudi og trúnni <lb break="yes"/>á hann til góds <unclear reason="hand"
                        hand="#student">sidsendir</unclear> á <unclear reason="hand" hand="#student"
                        >borgun00</unclear>. <lb break="yes"/><unclear reason="hand" hand="#student"
                        >Legufelagi</unclear> og til <unclear reason="hand" hand="#student"
                        >þess</unclear> ad halda gyd<lb break="no"/>íngum frá öllu samblandi vid <lb break="yes"/>adrar þjódir, og <unclear reason="hand" hand="#student"
                        >heitin</unclear> gud þeim <lb break="yes"/>launum sem <unclear reason="hand"
                        hand="#student">hlídníst</unclear> þeim; I stuttu <lb break="yes"/>máli er
                    lögmálid <unclear reason="hand" hand="#student">válir</unclear> guds er <lb break="yes"/>hann hefur byrt mönnunum á <lb break="yes"/>ymislegann hátt til
                    ad breyta <unclear reason="hand" hand="#student">eptir</unclear>,<lb/>bædi í
                        <unclear reason="hand" hand="#student">ordi</unclear> sínu og í
                        samviskulög<lb break="no"/>málinu sem ad er <unclear reason="hand"
                        hand="#student">raust</unclear> gud er <lb break="yes"/>í briósti mannanna er
                    ber <unclear reason="hand" hand="#student">verk</unclear> <lb break="yes"
                        /><unclear reason="hand" hand="#student">þeirra</unclear> saman vid guds
                        vilja; <pb facs="#image_028" n="2"/>vegna lögmálsins er <unclear
                        reason="hand" hand="#student">yfirtrodslun</unclear> <lb break="yes"/>ordin
                    kunn í heiminum, Jesú <unclear reason="hand" hand="#student">hefdu</unclear> <lb break="yes"/>menn ei þekt lögmálid; hefdi frá<lb break="no"/><unclear
                        reason="hand" hand="#student">fall </unclear>mannanna frá guds vilja
                        <unclear reason="hand" hand="#student">vanir</unclear> <lb break="yes"/>synd
                            <unclear><foreign xml:lang="gr"
                                >[a<add
                                place="above" hand="#student"
                    >c</add>paetia]</foreign></unclear> en ekki yfirtrodsla
                        <foreign xml:lang="gr"
                            >[paea<lb
                            break="no"/>basis]</foreign>
                    <unclear reason="hand" hand="#student">já</unclear> þad <unclear reason="hand"
                        hand="#student">meira</unclear> er lögmálid <lb break="yes"/><unclear
                        reason="hand" hand="#student">hratur</unclear>
                    <unclear reason="hand" hand="#student">meira</unclear> einsog til syndar, og
                        <unclear reason="hand" hand="#student">frá</unclear> <lb break="yes"/>kallar </p>
